snippet.title: Paradiddle V1.0 - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description: 50+ percussion instruments, 16 songs, 10 lessons, 3 new environments and a whole new look - with unlimited replay value. Paradiddle V1.0 arrives on Steam and Quest November 1st, 2022. Make sure you subscribe to us on YouTube and join our Discord (https://discord.gg/paradiddle) to be notified when V1 is live, and start your VR drumming journey!
